### Health Check
GET http://localhost:8080/api/actuator/health

### Swagger UI
GET http://localhost:8080/api/swagger-ui.html

### 1. Cadastrar novo ativo
POST http://localhost:8080/api/investments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "STOCK",
  "symbol": "BBAS3",
  "name": "Banco do Brasil",
  "quantity": 100,
  "purchasePrice": 56.80,
  "purchaseDate": "2024-07-31"
}

### 2. Listar todos os ativos
GET http://localhost:8080/api/investments

### 3. Filtrar por tipo
GET http://localhost:8080/api/investments?type=CRYPTO

### 4. Buscar por ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/investments/1

### 5. Buscar por símbolo
GET http://localhost:8080/api/investments/search?symbol=PETR

### 6. Atualizar ativo
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/investments/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "STOCK",
  "symbol": "PETR4",
  "name": "Petrobras PN Atualizado",
  "quantity": 150,
  "purchasePrice": 29.50,
  "purchaseDate": "2024-01-15"
}

### 7. Atualizar preço de mercado
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/investments/1/market-price?currentPrice=32.75

### 8. Obter resumo da carteira
GET http://localhost:8080/api/investments/summary

### 9. Remover ativo
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/investments/1

### 10. Cadastrar múltiplos ativos
POST http://localhost:8080/api/investments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "CRYPTO",
  "symbol": "ADA",
  "name": "Cardano",
  "quantity": 500,
  "purchasePrice": 2.30,
  "purchaseDate": "2024-08-15"
}

